modName: OSARE Maid Outfit Ultimate Tweaked Version
summary: Tweaked Maid Outfit based on OSARE Maid Outfit v1.1 with color black only.
descriptionHtml:
Anouncement :
All credits go to the original author \"anano\", let\'s thank him for all the wonderful mods he gave us.
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13569
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=12421


Modifications :
1. changed the outfit armor type from light armor to clothing,
2. added component \"Maid cat garter\" into the outfit set which is created by anano too,
3. \"Maid Amulet\" is now compactible with other jewlry necklaces,
4. all components are now enchantable,
5. other minor tweaks.


Notes :
1. work with DIMONIZED UNP female body
2. based on OSARE Maid Outfit v1.1 with color black only


Installation :
Unpack the contents to your Skyrim data folder.


Location :
Qasmoke(testing hall)
1 - [coc qasmoke] in the console,
2 - Buy it from the maid merchant,
3 - [coc Riverwood] in the console.
or you can just use the \"player.additem\" console command to acquire it.


Version :
1.1 - Maid garter fix
1.0 - Initial


Special thanks :
dimon99 for UNP
anano for the original mods

HAVE FUN !!!
author: alabataille
